type: ItemTurret
name: Vitreous
description: "Fires pressurized thermal beams that incinerate targets at medium range. Consumes slag and plastanium to maintain high-heat output."
size: 3
range: 152 
reload: 30 
shootCone: 15
rotateSpeed: 5
targetAir: true
